short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows GrabDuck search results side by side with Google, DuckDuckGo, Bing, or Yahoo results.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Currently we support next Search engines (where you will be able to see your Grabduck results):
- Google
- DuckDuckGo
- Bing
- Yahoo
